display_long_description:
FREE slice demo of I See Monsters 1. 

You have **only one night** to test your skills before the real challenge begins.

Welcome to the **I SEE MONSTERS 1 demo** — a sneak peek into the madness of **Willy Walee School** after dark. 🌙  

Your mission: **break into the school** and **steal the exam paper** without getting caught.  

But beware — **Mr. Funny** is already on patrol. He hears every step, every drop, and every wrong move. One slip, and it’s **24 hours in the lock-up**. 🔒  

Explore the school, try out a few puzzles, and see if you can crack the code to the Director’s office safe.

**Game Controls:** 🎮  
1. **Thumbstick**: Move around and rotate  
2. **Upper Buttons**: Crouch/Uncrouch  
3. **Lower Buttons**: Adjust your height

In this demo, **some items are placed in specific places ** to give you a taste of what’s to come.  

The full version features **changing item locations every round**, with unlimited combinations and **a whole bunch of stuff**!

You’ll experience **physics-based interactions** like picking up objects, unlocking doors, and sneaking through tight spots. 🕵️‍♂️  

This FREE demo is fully playable **standing or seated**, and you can adjust your height anytime.

**Estimated demo time**: **10–20 mins** — a perfect warm-up before the real heist. 💼
